pageProduct.name: WotNot Natural Organic Sensitive Facial Wipes All Skin Types 25
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Natural and organic face wipes for normal and sensitive skin.

Wotnot Face Wipes are 100% natural and biodegradable wipes that helps remove daily impurities and grime.

Contains Aloe Vera and sweet almond oil that has softening and moisturising properties that helps restore the lost moisture and calm itch and inflammation.

Contains certified organic rosehip oil that helps with skin regeneration and moisture re-balancing.

Formulated with vitamin E to help heal, nourish and protect the skin, leaving it smooth, supple and glowing.

Free from alcohol, artificial perfumes, parabens and petrochemicals.

Ideal for sensitive skin.

Can be used to remove makeup including waterproof mascara.

Ingredients

Purified water, caprylic/capric triglyceride (vegetable derived), glycerine (vegetable derived), cetearyl alcohol (plant derived), certified organic aloe vera*, certified organic sweet almond oil*, certified organic rosehip oil*, tocopherol acetate (vitamin e), cetearyl glucoside (plant derived), polyaminopropyl biguanide(extra mild preservative). 

*certified organic ingredients
